Package: qlip
Architecture: all
Depends: python3 (>= 3.8), python3-tk, ${misc:Depends}
Recommends: maim, slop, xdotool, x11-xserver-utils, grim, slurp, wmctrl, wlr-randr
Description: Lightweight screenshot utility for X11 and Wayland
 qlip captures screenshots with support for multi-monitor full-screen,
 interactive region selection, and per-window capture. Auto-detects
 X11 or Wayland session. Includes a GUI for settings and quick capture.
